---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQs | Finpoint"
  description="Frequently asked questions about Finpoint Funding — funding timelines, application fees, and available amounts."
  active="faqs"
>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="reveal">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="faq-list">
          <article class="faq-item reveal">
            <h2>How quickly can I receive funding?</h2>
            <p>
              Finpoint helps business owners by getting them access to funding as quickly as possible. With the appropriate information and documentation available it is possible to secure funding in as little as 24 hours. Business owners should make sure they provide all required documentation to ensure their application can be processed as quickly as possible. We take your privacy very seriously and can ensure that your information is managed securely.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item reveal">
            <h2>Are there application fees?</h2>
            <p>
              There are never any application or submission fees for creating and submitting a financing application with Finpoint.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item reveal">
            <h2>What is the maximum amount of money I can get from Finpoint?</h2>
            <p>
              Finpoint can arrange funding for amounts between $5,000 to $2,000,0000 -- all from one simple online application. Business owners can take multiple rounds of financing from Finpoint over time, as long as they qualify.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
